) 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[553,634,562,588]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="24">jemeni</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Brechtel" box="[642,820,562,588]" pageId="9" pageNumber="24" refString="Brechtel F. (2000) Neue Prachtkaferarten aus dem Jemen (Coleoptera, Buprestidae). Carolinea (Karlsruhe), 58, 227 - 230." type="journal article" year="2000">
